<section id="Section520511">
    <title>
      <anchor id="Anchor595526" role="Index"
              xreflabel="units of measure:capacity by class code;class codes:capacity uom details for"/>
      <indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>units of measure</primary>

        <secondary>capacity by class code</secondary>
      </indexterm> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>class codes</primary>

        <secondary>capacity uom details for</secondary>
      </indexterm>Capacity UOMs by Class Code</title>

    <para id="Para520512">To view a list of Capacity Units of Measure by Class
    Code, select the "Capacity UOMs by Class Code" option. The following
    screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para520516">
      <screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="images/PD_Disp_capUOMClass.png" id="Graphic563757"/>
            </imageobject>

            <caption id="Caption520517">Capacity UOMs by Class Code</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot>
   </para>

    <para id="Para520518">When displaying Capacity UOMs by Class Code, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para617093">All Class Codes</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193f9a8">
            <para>Select to display Capacity UOMs for all Class Codes.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520519">Selected</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193f9f0">
            <para>Specify Class Code whose Capacity UOMs you want to
          display.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para593278">Pattern</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193fa38">
            <para>Enter a Class Code pattern to select a range of Class
          Codes.</para>

            <para id="Para664844">Refine your search using Regular Expressions,
          as described in <link endterm="Anchor77806" id="XRef664843" linkend="Anchor77806"> Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions</link>"Topic: Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions".</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520523">Capacity UOMs</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193fa80">
            <para>Display lists Capacity UOMs by Class Code, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para520525">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520526">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193faec">
            <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para618304">QUERY</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193fb34">
            <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para664058">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193fb7c">
            <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para557059">Right-clicking on an Item in the Capacity UOMs list
    enables you to select from the following menu options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520529">Edit Item</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193fbe8">
            <para/>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml"
